deps/patches/2.17/
==================

Rebased patch series for pjsip 2.17. Opted into at build time:

    PJSIP_VERSION=2.17 ./get_dependencies.sh

The default (no env var, no positional arg) is still 2.12 and applies the
patch series at deps/patches/[0-9][0-9]_*.patch. The 2.17 path uses this
folder instead.

See PJSIP_217_MIGRATION.md at the repository root for the per-patch
verdicts, sequencing, and dropped/redirected items.

Numbering convention
--------------------
Keep the same NN_ prefixes as deps/patches/ so each patch is recognizable
across versions. A patch dropped from the 2.17 path simply does not exist
here; do not renumber. New 2.17-only patches use NN >= 40 to avoid
colliding with the 2.12 series.


